message:
@Chris_Huntley, regarding the title card fonts, I increased the fonts size of the groups mentioned in the beginning of the video, but left everything else the same because I can't duplicate the problem. The font size may depend on monitor resolution and the size the video is being viewed in. The video was recorded at 720p (1280x720), so adjusting the viewing size in YouTube may be the solution. I'll experiment with the font size in future videos and hopefully find a better solution.

Everyone, thanks for the feedback. Learning the software to create this type of video was effortless, but learning how to speak in front of the camera is another matter altogether.

Thanks again.
